TITLE: Request DTO with FromHeader Attribute
DESCRIPTION: Example of a request DTO class with a property decorated with [FromHeader] attribute for header value binding.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastendpoints/fastendpoints/blob/main/Src/Library/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
sealed class Request
{
    [FromHeader]
    public string Title { get; set; }
    public string FirstName { get; set; }
    public string LastName { get; set; }
}
```

