TITLE: Retrieving Endpoint Name in C#
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to get the auto-generated endpoint name using the GetName<T>() method for custom link generation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastendpoints/fastendpoints/blob/main/Src/Library/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
var endpointName = IEndpoint.GetName<SomeEndpoint>();
```

