TITLE: CSV Collection Property Binding
DESCRIPTION: Example of a request class supporting comma-separated value binding for collection properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastendpoints/fastendpoints/blob/main/Src/Library/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public class FindRequest
{
    [QueryParam]
    public string[] Status { get; set; }
}
```

