TITLE: Automatic Header Population in Tests
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates automatic header population in endpoint tests using the client POST method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastendpoints/fastendpoints/blob/main/Src/Library/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
var (rsp, res) = await App.Client.POSTAsync<MyEndpoint, Request, string>(
                     new()
                     {
                         Title = "Mrs.",
                         FirstName = "Doubt",
                         LastName = "Fire"
                     });
```

