TITLE: SendAcceptedAtAsync Usage
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to send a 202 Accepted response using SendCreatedAtAsync method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastendpoints/fastendpoints/blob/main/Src/Library/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
await SendCreatedAtAsync<ProgressEndpoint>(new { Id = "123" });
```

