TITLE: Disabling Automatic Header Population
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to disable automatic header population in endpoint tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastendpoints/fastendpoints/blob/main/Src/Library/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
POSTAsync<...>(..., populateHeaders: false);
```

